text: Barberino Tavarnelle is a comune in the Metropolitan City of Florence in the Italian region of Tuscany. It was created on 1 January 2019 from the former municipalities of Barberino Val d'Elsa and Tavarnelle Val di Pesa. ==References== ==Other website== * Official website Category:2019 establishments in Italy Category:Comunes in the Metropolitan City of Florence
title: Barberino Tavarnelle
